We'll stay overnight at the village.
It's inappropriate.

558
00:33:23,420 --> 00:33:24,880
How old is your soul

559
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:26,880
in this young body?

560
00:33:27,320 --> 00:33:29,940
You are adults. If you both agree,

561
00:33:29,940 --> 00:33:31,440
just let things happen

562
00:33:31,440 --> 00:33:33,010
as they should be.

563
00:33:33,510 --> 00:33:34,930
Furthermore, you've already slept
at Chu Nan's home.

564
00:33:35,260 --> 00:33:36,480
If I truly slept there,

565
00:33:36,480 --> 00:33:37,890
how can I know secrets of our boss?

566
00:33:39,980 --> 00:33:43,750
So you didn't stay at Chu Nan's home that night.

567
00:33:43,750 --> 00:33:45,190
You...you stayed at our boss's?

568
00:33:47,760 --> 00:33:48,310
Don't look at me.

569
00:33:48,310 --> 00:33:49,080
I just promised

570
00:33:49,080 --> 00:33:50,370
I wouldn't say any gossip of our boss.

571
00:33:50,370 --> 00:33:51,640
No way. Hurry up and tell us.

572
00:33:51,640 --> 00:33:52,920
Why did you go to our boss's home?

573
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:54,550
Where was Chu Nan? Why wasn't he with you?

574
00:33:54,550 --> 00:33:56,230
Our boss ruined your date,

575
00:33:56,230 --> 00:33:56,760
right?

576
00:33:56,760 --> 00:33:57,910
Remember, he has a girlfriend

577
00:33:57,910 --> 00:33:58,960
and an illegitimate child.

578
00:33:59,750 --> 00:34:00,600
Where is my crutch?

579
00:34:07,320 --> 00:34:09,560
Yun, tell me the truth.

580
00:34:10,540 --> 00:34:12,710
Where did you stay last night?

581
00:34:13,740 --> 00:34:14,790
Don't let your imagination run wild.

582
00:34:14,790 --> 00:34:16,400
Chu Nan lives with his parents.

583
00:34:18,960 --> 00:34:21,720
So you stayed with

584
00:34:21,720 --> 00:34:24,320
his parents last night?

585
00:34:25,500 --> 00:34:26,550
Sort of.

586
00:34:26,780 --> 00:34:29,270
It brought too much trouble to them.

587
00:34:29,780 --> 00:34:31,650
It is because of my dad and you.

588
00:34:31,650 --> 00:34:33,090
You went out without telling me.

589
00:34:34,520 --> 00:34:36,850
My daughter, are you Pigsy?

590
00:34:36,850 --> 00:34:38,370
You are making a false countercharge.

591
00:34:39,380 --> 00:34:40,850
It's you who lost the keys.

592
00:34:40,850 --> 00:34:42,790
How can you blame your dad and me!

593
00:34:44,540 --> 00:34:46,240
I've never seen anyone like you.

594
00:34:46,740 --> 00:34:48,900
Then tell me, what made your ankle
injured like this?

595
00:34:49,700 --> 00:34:51,700
It was just sprained.

596
00:34:52,780 --> 00:34:54,530
Mom, I remember

597
00:34:54,530 --> 00:34:55,640
I need to do overtime work.

598
00:34:58,620 --> 00:34:59,670
I know.

599
00:35:00,770 --> 00:35:02,070
I just want to tell you

600
00:35:02,530 --> 00:35:04,290
your dad will leave home
earlier tomorrow morning

601
00:35:04,290 --> 00:35:05,360
to attend a meeting at the suburb.

602
00:35:05,580 --> 00:35:07,540
You need to get to work by taxi.

603
00:35:08,080 --> 00:35:10,080
No need. I won't go to the company tomorrow.

604
00:35:12,880 --> 00:35:15,620
My daughter, you finally realized it.

605
00:35:15,620 --> 00:35:17,700
I've already told you

606
00:35:18,620 --> 00:35:21,840
the world will still rotate without you.

607
00:35:22,380 --> 00:35:24,500
Look at your ankle.

608
00:35:24,500 --> 00:35:26,870
I've told you to take two weeks off at home.

609
00:35:28,420 --> 00:35:30,710
Your company won't close down

610
00:35:30,710 --> 00:35:32,040
because of your break.

611
00:35:32,040 --> 00:35:33,360
It's not a break.

612
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:35,270
The workplace is changed to my home.

613
00:35:35,270 --> 00:35:36,470
My boss allowed me to

614
00:35:36,470 --> 00:35:38,280
work at home from tomorrow.

615
00:35:39,820 --> 00:35:42,340
Your boss is pretty thoughtful on this.

616
00:35:43,220 --> 00:35:45,270
It's because he feels guilty.

617
00:35:45,820 --> 00:35:46,550
What were you saying?

618
00:35:47,110 --> 00:35:47,810
Nothing.

619
00:35:47,810 --> 00:35:49,600
Mom, I'm going to do overtime work.

620
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:51,240
You're about to rest now.

621
00:35:51,890 --> 00:35:52,930
As you wish.

622
00:35:54,560 --> 00:35:55,830
Finished this bowl of soup.

623
00:35:56,610 --> 00:35:57,730
You needn't wash the bowl.

624
00:35:57,730 --> 00:35:58,050
Okay.

625
00:35:58,050 --> 00:35:59,280
I'll take it out tomorrow morning.

626
00:36:06,610 --> 00:36:08,020
Big pig hoot.

627
00:36:35,750 --> 00:36:36,450
Mr. Xia,

628
00:36:36,450 --> 00:36:38,290
I've sent the latest project progress
to your email box.

629
00:36:38,290 --> 00:36:39,300
Please check it out.

630
00:36:47,760 --> 00:36:48,560
You use the wrong font size.

631
00:36:50,120 --> 00:36:51,140
Sorry.

632
00:36:52,600 --> 00:36:55,400
Having a 3-hour video conferencing at weekend,

633
00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:57,640
I'm good enough to still keep breathing.

634
00:36:58,620 --> 00:36:59,600
Continue to correct it.

635
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:05,040
Mr. Xia, you must have other things to deal with.

636
00:37:05,540 --> 00:37:07,090
How about dealing with them first?

637
00:37:07,090 --> 00:37:08,710
I'll contact you after correcting all mistakes.

638
00:37:09,740 --> 00:37:11,330
No way. Correct them while holding the video call.

639
00:37:11,860 --> 00:37:13,030
You'll directly go to sleep

640
00:37:13,030 --> 00:37:14,150
after hanging up the call.

641
00:37:23,250 --> 00:37:25,190
Mr. Xia, it's time for dinner.

642
00:37:25,190 --> 00:37:26,530
Aren't you hungry?

643
00:37:26,530 --> 00:37:27,410
I'm stuffed by you.

644
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:31,510
I'll tell my parents

645
00:37:31,510 --> 00:37:32,690
to have dinner first.

646
00:37:35,250 --> 00:37:36,550
Chu Nan.

647
00:37:36,550 --> 00:37:38,280
Come in. Come in.

648
00:37:47,780 --> 00:37:49,700
Yun, Chu Nan is here.

649
00:37:52,100 --> 00:37:54,020
Why are you still standing there?

650
00:37:54,020 --> 00:37:55,040
Hurry up.

651
00:38:01,460 --> 00:38:03,590
Quickly. Put on your clothes.

652
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:05,780
Why is he here?

653
00:38:06,200 --> 00:38:07,620
I called him to come.

654
00:38:07,620 --> 00:38:09,160
You bothered him a few days ago

655
00:38:09,160 --> 00:38:10,850
for staying at his home overnight.

656
00:38:10,850 --> 00:38:13,250
We're supposed to invite him to our home.

657
00:38:13,250 --> 00:38:15,760
We should ask him to dinner
just like how he treated you.

658
00:38:15,760 --> 00:38:17,360
Why didn't you tell me?

659
00:38:17,360 --> 00:38:18,560
I've told you.

660
00:38:18,560 --> 00:38:19,960
When?

661
00:38:19,960 --> 00:38:21,360
This afternoon.

662
00:38:22,460 --> 00:38:24,450
I knocked at your door this afternoon

663
00:38:24,450 --> 00:38:26,760
and asked "How about inviting Chu Nan for dinner?".

664
00:38:26,760 --> 00:38:28,470
You said it was okay.

665
00:38:28,470 --> 00:38:29,280
Now you...

666
00:38:29,280 --> 00:38:31,120
I didn't talk to you.

667
00:38:31,120 --> 00:38:33,520
I was having a video conference with my boss.

668
00:38:34,630 --> 00:38:35,890
You closed your door.

669
00:38:35,890 --> 00:38:37,640
How could I know you were
having a video conference?

670
00:38:37,910 --> 00:38:38,760
It's so...

671
00:38:38,760 --> 00:38:39,990
Fine. Fine.

672
00:38:39,990 --> 00:38:41,080
Now he is here.

673
00:38:41,080 --> 00:38:42,610
It's just a common meal.

674
00:38:42,610 --> 00:38:44,500
Hurry up. Put on your clothes and get out.

675
00:38:44,500 --> 00:38:45,840
Don't make him wait for a long time.

676
00:38:45,840 --> 00:38:46,500
Quick!

677
00:38:50,370 --> 00:38:51,970
She'll come out in a moment.

678
00:38:53,040 --> 00:38:54,080
You don't need to.

679
00:38:54,500 --> 00:38:56,790
We just invite you for dinner.
You don't need to bring presents.

680
00:38:56,790 --> 00:38:58,290
No, no. I don't know what to bring

681
00:38:58,290 --> 00:38:59,970
so I bought Mr. Xing and you some nourishment.

682
00:39:00,560 --> 00:39:01,970
It's very kind of you.

683
00:39:02,560 --> 00:39:03,360
Xing!

684
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:05,510
Come here. Let me introduce him to you.

685
00:39:06,920 --> 00:39:09,140
This is Chu Nan.

686
00:39:09,140 --> 00:39:10,370
This is Yun's dad.

687
00:39:12,800 --> 00:39:14,440
Nice to meet you, Mr. Xing. I'm Chu Nan.

688
00:39:19,380 --> 00:39:20,580
What are you doing?

689
00:39:21,910 --> 00:39:23,990
Chu Nan, come here and have a seat.

690
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:25,010
Have a seat.

691
00:39:32,020 --> 00:39:33,010
Hi, Chu Nan.

692
00:39:33,680 --> 00:39:34,850
Is your ankle okay?

693
00:39:34,850 --> 00:39:35,560
No big problem.

694
00:39:35,940 --> 00:39:36,930
That will be great.

695
00:39:36,930 --> 00:39:38,450
It's a serious injury!
How can it be "no big problem"?

696
00:39:40,160 --> 00:39:41,380
Do you think it's not a big problem

697
00:39:41,380 --> 00:39:42,870
until my daughter's ankle is broken?

698
00:39:43,840 --> 00:39:45,140
Dad, you misunderstood.

699
00:39:45,140 --> 00:39:46,840
My injury has truly nothing to do with Chu Nan.

700
00:39:46,840 --> 00:39:48,260
Nothing to do with him?

701
00:39:49,340 --> 00:39:51,750
He took you to his home that night.

702
00:39:51,750 --> 00:39:54,120
Your ankle was good before you left home.

703
00:39:54,120 --> 00:39:55,860
But when you came back,
it had been sprained.

704
00:39:55,860 --> 00:39:57,200
If it's not his business, then whose?

705
00:39:58,710 --> 00:39:59,840
Enough.

706
00:40:00,210 --> 00:40:02,260
We invited Chu Nan for dinner.

707
00:40:02,260 --> 00:40:03,910
Why were you talking about this?

708
00:40:03,910 --> 00:40:04,680
Come here. Have a seat.

709
00:40:05,420 --> 00:40:06,550
Have a seat.

710
00:40:08,240 --> 00:40:10,530
Chu Nan, actually

711
00:40:10,530 --> 00:40:12,760
it's Yun who should be blamed.

712
00:40:13,030 --> 00:40:14,820
After she came back that day,

713
00:40:14,820 --> 00:40:16,610
we asked her what had happened.

714
00:40:16,610 --> 00:40:17,880
But she said nothing

715
00:40:17,880 --> 00:40:20,440
and directly went into her room
to do overtime work.

716
00:40:21,720 --> 00:40:22,790
She is so...

717
00:40:22,790 --> 00:40:25,090
In fact, that night...

718
00:40:25,090 --> 00:40:26,870
I indeed didn't take good care of Xing Yun that night.

719
00:40:28,060 --> 00:40:30,500
I'm truly sorry, Mr. and Mrs. Xing.

720
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:37,490
It's all my fault.

721
00:40:37,490 --> 00:40:38,880
I asked her to go out and have fun.

722
00:40:40,340 --> 00:40:41,380
So what did you do

723
00:40:42,200 --> 00:40:44,560
that made her injured like this?

724
00:40:45,890 --> 00:40:46,440
Rock-climbing.

725
00:40:49,040 --> 00:40:49,720
You?

726
00:40:54,800 --> 00:40:56,340
What a good news!

727
00:40:56,340 --> 00:40:58,200
My daughter can do rock-climbing!

728
00:40:59,200 --> 00:41:02,020
She stays at home after school
or work all these years.

729
00:41:02,020 --> 00:41:03,270
Her motor nerves

730
00:41:03,270 --> 00:41:05,460
have already degraded into nuclei.

731
00:41:05,810 --> 00:41:07,700
But... you took her to do rock-climbing?

732
00:41:07,700 --> 00:41:09,910
It's a good thing.

733
00:41:09,910 --> 00:41:12,200
But remember to be careful

734
00:41:12,200 --> 00:41:14,770
when you exercise outdoors next time.
Safety comes first.

735
00:41:14,770 --> 00:41:15,700
I know, Mrs. Xing.

736
00:41:16,710 --> 00:41:18,880
Mr. Xing, I was negligent this time.

737
00:41:19,460 --> 00:41:20,820
I understand your feelings.

738
00:41:20,820 --> 00:41:22,180
I'll definitely pay much more attention next time

739
00:41:22,180 --> 00:41:23,160
to ensure Xing Yun's safety.

740
00:41:24,080 --> 00:41:24,880
That's right.

741
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:27,560
Your daughter stays at home

742
00:41:27,560 --> 00:41:29,880
to do overwork or watch anime after work.

743
00:41:30,310 --> 00:41:31,430
She doesn't exercise at all.

744
00:41:31,430 --> 00:41:32,660
How can she keep healthy?

745
00:41:32,880 --> 00:41:34,310
Now there is a person

746
00:41:34,310 --> 00:41:36,280
persuading her to exercise outdoors

747
00:41:36,280 --> 00:41:38,310
and enjoy life. It's a good thing.

748
00:41:38,310 --> 00:41:39,970
But you should do it step by step.

749
00:41:41,540 --> 00:41:43,320
Yes, you are right. I was too hasty.

750
00:41:44,500 --> 00:41:45,400
Remember,

751
00:41:45,750 --> 00:41:48,290
if you are going to do dangerous exercise
like this in the future,

752
00:41:48,290 --> 00:41:50,630
be sure to tell your parents in advance.

753
00:41:50,630 --> 00:41:51,060
Am I right?

754
00:41:51,060 --> 00:41:51,410
Yes, of course.

755
00:41:51,410 --> 00:41:52,050
Did you listen to me?

756
00:41:52,260 --> 00:41:53,160
Yes, I heard that.

757
00:41:53,160 --> 00:41:55,280
Well, enough education.

758
00:41:55,280 --> 00:41:57,400
Are you going to make us eat cold food?

759
00:41:57,400 --> 00:41:59,520
I'll get the rice for you.

760
00:41:59,520 --> 00:42:00,390
Let's start.

761
00:42:01,160 --> 00:42:02,040
-You are so... -Thank you, Mrs. Xing.

762
00:42:02,040 --> 00:42:03,720
You're welcome. Help yourself.

763
00:42:31,140 --> 00:42:32,220
Did you draw this?

764
00:42:34,500 --> 00:42:36,100
It's my first time to see your drawing.

765
00:42:37,920 --> 00:42:38,770
You are awesome.

766
00:42:41,900 --> 00:42:44,720
Don't you have anything want to ask?

767
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:47,090
You mean the thing mentioned just now?

768
00:42:49,330 --> 00:42:50,160
I think you don't want to cause troubles

769
00:42:50,160 --> 00:42:51,680
so you didn't tell much to your parents.

770
00:42:53,860 --> 00:42:57,360
Actually I called you that day

771
00:42:57,360 --> 00:42:58,840
and sent messages to you.

772
00:42:59,860 --> 00:43:00,800
I've received them.

773
00:43:01,180 --> 00:43:02,560
You said you ran into an accident.

774
00:43:04,450 --> 00:43:05,240
Is that this?

775
00:43:05,910 --> 00:43:08,200
Yes. In fact, on my way to

776
00:43:08,200 --> 00:43:09,840
see my boss that day,

777
00:43:10,120 --> 00:43:11,430
I ran into human trafficking.

778
00:43:11,660 --> 00:43:12,520
Human trafficking?

779
00:43:12,520 --> 00:43:13,460
I was fine.

780
00:43:13,460 --> 00:43:15,680
But my bag was robbed by human traffickers.

781
00:43:15,680 --> 00:43:18,320
My identification, keys and money
were all in that bag.

782
00:43:19,180 --> 00:43:20,690
I also lost my laptop.

783
00:43:24,280 --> 00:43:25,160
I see.

784
00:43:25,160 --> 00:43:26,470
Sorry. I should have driven you there.

785
00:43:26,470 --> 00:43:28,000
No, no. It's not your fault.

786
00:43:28,000 --> 00:43:29,400
I was too careless.

787
00:43:30,960 --> 00:43:33,730
But don't you want to know

788
00:43:33,730 --> 00:43:36,130
where I slept that night?
